configure 0.0.1 release notes
-----------------------------

configure automatically generated Makefiles from a project definition file.

configure is Copyright (c) 2004 Pierre Pronchery
It is shipped under the terms of the GPL license, which you may read in the
COPYING file also contained in this archive.

Please read the INSTALL file for instructions about how to compile and install
configure.

Please read the BUGS file for information about known problems, and planned
feature upgrades.

Thanks for using this program. I hope it will be useful.
